file1.highlighted_code: def gcd(a, b): while(b != 0): tmp = a % b a = b b = tmp return a n = int(input()) lst = list(map(int, input().split())) for i in range(len(lst)): for j in range(i + 1, len(lst)): if gcd(lst[i], lst[j] == 1): print(lst[i], lst[j], end = "\n")
